            Original Traveller Rules - (c) 1986

I couldn\'t find a specific reference here - however the chassis
configuration table on page 27 is what I would use as a guide.

Configuration           Weight Mod      Price Mod       Armor
----
Open Frame              0.5             0.5             None
Box/Wedge               -               -               Mesh
Cylinder/Cone           -               1.1             Mesh
