Miscellaneous Information Addendum:
 
 - To program the Hos-Jar\'s brain, Difficult (Computer), 20 min.  
   [One level lower if the manual is used w/task, 10 min.)
 
 - To program the sensors, Easy (Computer), 10 min.
 
