    'from' => 'Erich Schneider',
    'body' => 'Re: what are the Ine Givar up to...

In _Survival Margin_, covering the end of the Rebellion period, there
are a few entries covering Ine Givar activities on Rhylanor (a student
demonstration) and Regina (a bomb strike at a mall near where Norris
was supposed to visit). Their press releases always referred to
Archduke Norris as "Duke Norris" and were filled with phrases like
"the moment for democracy is now!". These incidents were followed by a
statement by Zhodani envoy Shtebifriashav who said that the Zhodani
