passangers to live on. Keep in mind, the point where I was visulizing it 
from was the \'keel\' of the ship. So I got a full view of the things size 
and just pictured it landing on top of me.
 The Armored Cruiser would be no strech for 240crew(if the number 
survives conversion, wich is in doubt). Seeing as how it is 280m and the 
Scout is 42m.
 From being on a 38ft sail boat -vs- (my Grandparents) new 42ft sail boat 
it\'s obvious to me what a diffrince a few m can make.

